                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Ambassador <persName type="to">Meyer</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-05-21">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 21, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Bacon directs Mr. Meyer to urge authorities to identify and punish
                    murderers; also directs him to ask the British consul to take charge of the
                    American interests and the American consulate at Batum. Mr. Bacon states that
                    the British Government has been asked to give permission.)</p>
            </div>
